
* If user want to generate contiunes numbers between some of the ranges will use the below code line to generate to automatic numbers. 
* Enumerable.Range(startrange, endrange) this code line will generate the automatic numbers between the ranges.

VB.NET
============
Dim numbers As IEnumerable(Of Integer) = Enumerable.Range(1, 10000) ' number generation


For i as integer =0 to numbers.count-1
 Console.Writeline(numbers(i))
Next


